<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1397,1642]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,423,1546,1572]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">General distribution:</emphasis>
Widespread throughout the east from Quebec, 
<collectingCountry box="[995,1085,1546,1572]" name="Canada" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Canada</collectingCountry>
and Maine, south to Florida, and west to Minnesota, Michigan, the Great Plains to Kansas, and southern Arizona. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,304,1615,1641]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Larval host:</emphasis>
